{
  "stem": "22892.4",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I couldn't even use my fingers because it was-- and I forgot-- there is a name for that sickness, [NON-ENGLISH], you know, eaten by lice and, and filth and dirt.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And this is what came about.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I end up in a hospital, in, in, in Lutsk hospital.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And there was also a lot of soldiers in that hospital.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they treat it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I don't know how I got into the hospital, to be honest with you.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I mean, I just-- but I do remember being there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "The first night-- the first night, I was in a room when they brought in a, a woman, a young woman, I guess, a young mother that was drinking wooden alcohol.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And she died in that room.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I was with-- all night in the same room.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Then the next day, there was a Russian officer came-- who was in that room with me.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I remember there were airplanes bombarding.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And at that time, it didn't bother me if they-- if they-- if they drop a bomb, and I get killed.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I, I didn't fear that at all.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "So when we-- you know, thinking about dying, that part wasn't so bad.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "[SIGHS] I stayed in the hospital for a few days.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And then this officer who's with me in the room-- I mean, he's a nice man.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And I thought maybe I could stick with him or something.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "I mean, I always tried to leech onto somebody.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "I, I, I look for somebody.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And he says, you can't be with me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "He says, I have to go on the front line.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "In fact, there's-- two or three soldiers came in.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And, and they-- and he, he got dressed.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And he was leaving.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
